title: 222: My Dream Job
itunes:title: 222: My Dream Job
description:
On this week's episode, it's the season 2 finale, Bill's directorial debut on the Scrubs series, and the crew has become disillusioned with their dream career. In the real world, Zach and Donald continue. their plan to get Joelle a partner, Zach reveals the time he flew to Las Vegas for a bottle of water.
